1255
01:39:35.142 --> 01:39:36.560
Get away from my fish.

1256
01:39:38.437 --> 01:39:40.314
[growls]

1257
01:39:41.773 --> 01:39:43.400
Keibu.

1258
01:39:48.405 --> 01:39:49.907
[Grogu sighs]

1259
