Fall back!

1326
01:50:17.492 --> 01:50:18.327
[groans]

1327
01:50:22.039 --> 01:50:25.125
[machinery whirring. beeping]

1328
01:50:41.058 --> 01:50:42.643
[shouts. grunts]

1329
01:50:43.268 --> 01:50:44.269
[exclaims]

1330
01:50:44.353 --> 01:50:45.395
[♪ tense music plays]

1331
01:50:46.188 --> 01:50:47.689
[grunting]

1332
01:50:51.902 --> 01:50:53.028
[grunts]

1333
01:51:16.510 --> 01:51:19.012
[device beeping]

1334
01:51:27.646 --> 01:51:28.522
[groans]

1335
01:51:30.816 --> 01:51:31.900
[grunts]

1336
01:51:36.530 --> 01:51:37.990
[babbles]

1337
01:51:45.622 --> 01:51:47.749
[devices beeping]

1338
01:52:06.143 --> 01:52:07.352
[grunts]

1339
01:52:08.145 --> 01:52:09.396
[electricity crackling]

1340
01:52:09.479 --> 01:52:10.564
[metal creaking]

1341
01:52:12.858 --> 01:52:13.984
[electricity crackles]

1342
01:52:15.152 --> 01:52:16.403
[babbles]

1343
01:52:17.613 --> 01:52:19.448
[♪ gentle music plays]

1344
01:52:31.293 --> 01:52:33.128
[speaks Huttese]

1345
01:52:33.212 --> 01:52:34.922
[Hutt Sister speaks Huttese]

1346
01:52:35.005 --> 01:52:37.090
[in Huttese] Wait! We know much.

1347
01:52:37.174 --> 01:52:38.675
Go help Rotta.

1348
01:52:40.344 --> 01:52:41.887
[Hutt Brother speaks Huttese]

1349
01:52:41.970 --> 01:52:44.515
-[Hutt Brother speaks Huttese]
-[Hutt Sister speaks Huttese]

1350
01:52:45.807 --> 01:52:46.808
[speaks Huttese]

1351
01:52:46.892 --> 01:52:48.435
You saw my face.

1352
01:52:49.353 --> 01:52:50.103
[in Huttese] Stop!

1353
01:52:50.187 --> 01:52:51.021
[Hutt Sister gasping]

1354
01:52:51.104 --> 01:52:52.606
Now it's time to die.

1355
01:53:02.491 --> 01:53:03.534
[grunts]

1356
01:53:08.580 --> 01:53:09.790
[grunts]

1357
01:53:12.125 --> 01:53:14.545
[♪ majestic music plays]

1358
01:53:15.963 --> 01:53:17.005
[machinery powers down]

1359
01:53:17.673 --> 01:53:19.007
[sighs]

1360
01:53:20.717 --> 01:53:22.219
[♪ tense music plays]

1361
01:53:28.809 --> 01:53:29.810
[Embo grunts]

1362
01:53:31.854 --> 01:53:33.355
[both grunting]

1363
01:53:34.022 --> 01:53:34.898
[Embo grunts]

1364
01:53:37.609 --> 01:53:39.069
[The Mandalorian shouts]

1365
01:53:40.696 --> 01:53:42.447
[Embo grunting]

1366
01:53:44.491 --> 01:53:45.492
[both grunt]

1367
01:53:46.869 --> 01:53:48.620
[Grogu exclaims. groans]

1368
01:53:50.080 --> 01:53:51.331
[Hutt Brother growls]

1369
01:53:54.042 --> 01:53:55.335
[grunts]

1370
01:53:56.044 --> 01:53:58.213
-[whimpers]
-[slurps]

1371
01:53:58.297 --> 01:53:59.673
[growls]

1372
01:54:00.591 --> 01:54:01.633
[growls]

1373
01:54:01.717 --> 01:54:02.801
[in English] Leave him alone!

1374
01:54:04.511 --> 01:54:05.512
[groans]

1375
01:54:06.263 --> 01:54:08.182
[both grunting. roaring]

1376
01:54:13.854 --> 01:54:14.688
[grunts]

1377
01:54:16.857 --> 01:54:17.691
[grunts]

1378
01:54:18.984 --> 01:54:20.402
[weapon clatters]

1379
01:54:22.487 --> 01:54:24.281
[grunts. pants]

1380
01:54:24.990 --> 01:54:27.784
[in Huttese]
You don't have Jabba to protect you.

1381
01:54:28.368 --> 01:54:29.828
I'm not little anymore!

1382
01:54:32.164 --> 01:54:33.790
[all grunting]

1383
01:54:41.465 --> 01:54:42.466
[snarls]

1384
01:54:43.217 --> 01:54:44.218
[growls]

1385
01:54:45.427 --> 01:54:46.428
[Embo grunts]

1386
01:54:50.182 --> 01:54:51.266
[The Mandalorian grunts]

1387
01:54:53.936 --> 01:54:56.647
[growling]

1388
01:54:57.356 --> 01:54:58.190
[snarls]

1389
01:55:03.153 --> 01:55:04.238
[Force rumbling]

1390
01:55:15.666 --> 01:55:17.543
[both grunting]

1391
01:55:20.921 --> 01:55:22.589
[Rotta shouts]

1392
01:55:32.140 --> 01:55:34.142
[♪ gentle music plays]

1393
01:55:34.226 --> 01:55:35.602
[Keibu snoring]

1394
01:55:37.521 --> 01:55:39.398
[both grunting]

1395
01:55:40.524 --> 01:55:41.358
[grunts]

1396
01:55:45.571 --> 01:55:46.405
[Embo grunts]

1397
01:55:48.115 --> 01:55:49.283
[snarls]

1398
01:55:52.452 --> 01:55:54.413
[Hutt Brother. Rotta grunting]

1399
01:56:01.170 --> 01:56:04.423
[in Huttese] Stop! You'll kill us all!

1400
01:56:05.632 --> 01:56:07.259
[Hutts yell]

1401
01:56:13.307 --> 01:56:15.809
[Force rumbling]

1402
01:56:15.893 --> 01:56:19.313
[♪ uplifting music plays]

1403
01:56:34.453 --> 01:56:35.537
[gasps]

1404
01:56:42.085 --> 01:56:44.922
[both groaning]

1405
01:56:47.257 --> 01:56:48.634
[roars]

1406
01:56:49.009 --> 01:56:50.552
[in Huttese] Save us. bounty hunter!

1407
01:56:51.929 --> 01:56:52.930
Keibu. [speaks Kyuzo]

1408
01:56:53.013 --> 01:56:54.681
[in Huttese] Save us!

1409
01:56:55.224 --> 01:56:57.184
[Hutt Brother speaks Huttese]

1410
01:56:57.893 --> 01:56:59.853
[Hutt Brother exclaims]

1411
01:57:00.395 --> 01:57:02.147
-[screams]
-[Hutt brother groaning]

1412
01:57:07.110 --> 01:57:08.403
[groans]

1413
01:57:09.738 --> 01:57:10.739
[screams]

1414
01:57:21.959 --> 01:57:23.377
[metal banging]

1415
01:57:23.460 --> 01:57:25.212
[♪ tense music plays]

1416
01:57:26.755 --> 01:57:28.507
[banging continues]

1417
01:57:29.049 --> 01:57:31.718
We don't have much time.
We have to get out of here.

1418
01:57:32.678 --> 01:57:33.887
Is there another way out?

1419
01:57:33.971 --> 01:57:36.640
-I think it's that way.
-Go. Go!

1420
01:57:53.156 --> 01:57:54.074
Target sighted.

1421
01:57:54.950 --> 01:57:55.784
[droid yells]

1422
01:58:18.348 --> 01:58:20.017
[static on comms]

1423
01:58:20.100 --> 01:58:21.018
Hello?

1424
01:58:21.101 --> 01:58:22.978
[Anzellan 1 through comms]
Mando! We came back.

1425
01:58:23.061 --> 01:58:24.313
-What?
-We came back.

1426
01:58:24.396 --> 01:58:26.106
We told you we would.

1427
01:58:26.190 --> 01:58:28.192
[♪ hopeful music plays]

1428
01:58:33.155 --> 01:58:36.116
[Ward] Adelphi Squadron.
entering atmosphere.

1429
01:58:37.075 --> 01:58:39.786
-What's your status. Mando?
-We're under attack.

1430
01:58:40.787 --> 01:58:42.122
There are too many.

1431
01:58:42.206 --> 01:58:44.208
Fire everything you have
at my location.

1432
01:58:45.751 --> 01:58:48.962
-[Ward] Your location?
-Yes. my location.

1433
01:58:49.046 --> 01:58:50.547
I can't give that order.

1434
01:58:50.631 --> 01:58:52.049
Don't worry...

1435
01:58:54.051 --> 01:58:56.261
we'll be out of here
by the time you do.

1436
01:58:57.888 --> 01:58:58.931
Good luck.

1437
01:58:59.014 --> 01:59:00.390
[X-wing engines screeching]

1438
01:59:02.518 --> 01:59:03.810
Blue Leader to squadron.

1439
01:59:04.394 --> 01:59:07.439
assume defensive formation.
prepare to engage.

1440
01:59:07.523 --> 01:59:08.690
All weapons hot.

1441
01:59:08.774 --> 01:59:09.608
Copy that.

1442
01:59:21.411 --> 01:59:23.038
[droid chatter]

1443
01:59:27.251 --> 01:59:29.002
Enemy fighters approaching.

1444
01:59:29.086 --> 01:59:31.088
[♪ heroic music plays]

1445
01:59:31.171 --> 01:59:32.047
Here they come.

1446
01:59:39.930 --> 01:59:41.181
[Rotta grunting]

1447
01:59:41.849 --> 01:59:42.933
[Rotta roars]

1448
01:59:43.016 --> 01:59:44.226
[droid beeps]

1449
01:59:53.735 --> 01:59:54.862
[chuckles]

1450
01:59:59.366 --> 02:00:00.701
Turbolasers. up ahead.

1451
02:00:00.784 --> 02:00:01.952
Got it.

1452
02:00:22.848 --> 02:00:24.266
I've got one on my tail.

1453
02:00:26.977 --> 02:00:28.478
I got you.

1454
02:00:34.484 --> 02:00:35.485
[squeaks]

1455
02:00:38.655 --> 02:00:40.282
-[cheers]
-Yippee! Yay!

1456
02:00:40.365 --> 02:00:41.950
Taking out the launch tubes.

1457
02:00:49.708 --> 02:00:52.586
Blue Leader to Red Jammer.
mark it and lock it in.

1458
02:00:55.088 --> 02:00:56.215
Locking in target.

1459
02:00:59.927 --> 02:01:00.969
It's a dead end.

1460
02:01:02.262 --> 02:01:03.680
We're trapped.

1461
02:01:04.389 --> 02:01:05.599
Stand back.

1462
02:01:11.980 --> 02:01:13.315
[Ward through comms]
We're closing fast.

1463
02:01:13.398 --> 02:01:14.816
Repeat. we're closing fast.

1464
02:01:14.900 --> 02:01:16.485
You better be
out of there. Mando.

1465
02:01:16.568 --> 02:01:17.986
[The Mandalorian] Jump.

1466
02:01:18.070 --> 02:01:20.155
[Rotta]
That's a long way down.

1467
02:01:20.239 --> 02:01:21.448
Closing on target.

1468
02:01:22.991 --> 02:01:25.285
-[The Mandalorian] Gotta jump.
-[Rotta] Moat's not that deep.

1469
02:01:25.369 --> 02:01:27.412
It's a bomber. Jump.

1470
02:01:27.496 --> 02:01:29.289
Let's light up this swamp.

1471
02:01:40.384 --> 02:01:41.677
[yelling]

1472
02:02:04.116 --> 02:02:05.742
[pilot]
Anybody got eyes on Mando?

1473
02:02:06.410 --> 02:02:07.411
There they are.

1474
02:02:07.995 --> 02:02:10.289
[♪ uplifting music plays]

1475
02:02:11.832 --> 02:02:15.586
Zeb. go collect the trash.

1476
02:02:23.719 --> 02:02:26.513
I'm getting a little tired
of these hot extractions.

1477
02:02:27.431 --> 02:02:29.391
-What took you so long?
-[Grogu babbles]

1478
02:02:29.474 --> 02:02:30.642
[chuckles]

1479
02:02:30.726 --> 02:02:31.852
Hop in.

1480
02:02:31.935 --> 02:02:33.770
Let's head home.

1481
02:02:39.109 --> 02:02:41.111
[♪ triumphant music plays]

1482
02:02:56.710 --> 02:02:58.086
Colonel.

1483
02:03:00.422 --> 02:03:01.798
Messy.

1484
02:03:02.382 --> 02:03:03.634
Very messy.

1485
02:03:04.843 --> 02:03:06.470
Why'd you come for me?

1486
02:03:06.553 --> 02:03:08.055
That wasn't part
of the mission.

1487
02:03:08.805 --> 02:03:11.934
You were right.
Coin told us everything.

1488
02:03:12.434 --> 02:03:14.061
The Twins were playing us.

1489
02:03:14.144 --> 02:03:16.688
Feeding information
to the Empire all along.

1490
02:03:18.023 --> 02:03:20.692
They picked a side.
It wasn't ours.

1491
02:03:21.318 --> 02:03:24.947
Besides.
we don't leave our own behind.

1492
02:03:25.489 --> 02:03:27.282
I'm an independent contractor.

1493
02:03:27.366 --> 02:03:30.327
Sure. Mando. Sure you are.

1494
02:03:30.410 --> 02:03:31.787
[Grogu exclaims]

1495
02:03:41.004 --> 02:03:42.923
Can I give you a ride
somewhere?

1496
02:03:43.006 --> 02:03:45.217
Actually. I was thinking
I could stay here.

1497
02:03:46.009 --> 02:03:47.803
Maybe work
for the New Republic.

1498
02:03:48.387 --> 02:03:50.806
Don't take this
the wrong way. but...

1499
02:03:50.889 --> 02:03:52.975
I'm not sure you would fit in.

1500
02:03:53.058 --> 02:03:54.893
You know... [grunts]

1501
02:03:54.977 --> 02:03:57.229
...I might have
a uniform that would fit him.

1502
02:03:58.272 --> 02:04:01.149
Come on.
let me buy you a drink.

1503
02:04:02.943 --> 02:04:05.487
Thank you. Mando.
I owe you big time.

1504
02:04:05.571 --> 02:04:06.905
Just doing my job.

1505
02:04:07.531 --> 02:04:08.532
And keep an eye on him.

1506
02:04:09.658 --> 02:04:11.285
Your dad's
one of the good ones.

1507
02:04:11.368 --> 02:04:12.369
[coos]

1508
02:04:23.422 --> 02:04:25.674
[Anzellans chattering
indistinctly]

1509
02:04:25.757 --> 02:04:27.050
Come on. big guy.

1510
02:04:28.218 --> 02:04:30.596
[Anzellan 2] Watch your step.
First round's on me.

1511
02:04:35.142 --> 02:04:36.643
[♪ wistful music plays]

1512
02:04:39.771 --> 02:04:41.899
Hey. kid. Come up here.

1513
02:04:41.982 --> 02:04:43.025
[coos]

1514
02:04:48.488 --> 02:04:49.489
[grunts]

1515
02:05:01.585 --> 02:05:02.794
[The Mandalorian] Your turn.

1516
02:05:05.714 --> 02:05:06.715
Go ahead.

1517
02:05:18.310 --> 02:05:20.312
[♪ epic music plays]

1518
02:05:34.618 --> 02:05:37.955
[♪ "The Mandalorian"
theme plays]

1519
02:06:29.923 --> 02:06:32.259
[♪ electronic music plays]

1520
02:07:42.496 --> 02:07:45.374
[♪ ominous music plays]

1521
02:08:13.151 --> 02:08:16.905
[♪ gentle music plays]

1522
02:09:18.383 --> 02:09:21.762
[♪ dramatic music plays]

1523
02:09:36.443 --> 02:09:38.445
[♪ dramatic music continues]

1524
02:10:36.086 --> 02:10:38.922
[♪ guitar version of
"The Mandalorian" theme plays]

1524
02:10:39.305 --> 02:11:39.789
